ore, pricked with a needle, they yeeld bloudy drop<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">; And at the first spreading of this dreadfull dis<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">se in Poland, all that cut off this <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">orrible and snakie haire, lost their eyes, or the humour fall<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">g dow<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">e upon other parts of the body&punc; tortur'd them extremely. Heare my Author, that learned and famous Professour of Physicks in</HI> Padua, Hercules Saxonia, <HI>in his <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">wue word:</HI> Plica, est agglutinatio, vel invis<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">atio quaedam pilorum ex humido visei|do, lento ac glutinoso. Nunc primum peruniversam fer&egrave; Poloniam grassatur; i<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">&ograve; ver&ograve; per quasdam Germaniae partes divagatur&mdash;Maximam partem <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">oeminas in&punc; vadit: Eos etiam qui <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">orriginem capitis, quam vulgus tineam vocat, medicamentis <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">epercutientibus represserunt: Praetere&agrave; f<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">minas, quae menstruis temporibus nonsa|tis purgantur.&mdash;Quis non novum, mirabile, &amp; horridum putet capillos ex pro|p<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ia natur&acirc; planos, denussos a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters"> simplices, momento temporis sponte su&acirc; sub coelo admodum <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">gido incrispari, paulo post e<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">igi, involvi, at&abque; indissolubili<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">er conjun|gi, va<GAP DESC="il