pex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ium s<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ei <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 word"> extingua<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">as; ne qualis sit, tandem experia|mur. <HI>Idem Ibid&punc; Thesi</HI> 51.</NOTE> to dispute, or go about to determine: neither is it much materiall for my purpose. For, be it whether it will, it is infinitely horrible and ins<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">fferable beyond all compasse of conceipt, and above the reach either of humane or Angelicall thoughts. It doth not onely exceed with an in|comparable disproportion <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ll possibility of pati|ence and resistance; but also even ability to beare it; and yet notwithstanding, it must upon necessi|ty be borne so long as GOD is GOD. Take in a word, all that I intend to tell you in the point at
